text: Esbela da Fonseca (born 26 July 1942) is a Portuguese gymnast. She competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics, the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Portugal Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lisbon
